B.aov=new A.KY("UniFind is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and how we keep it safe.",null)
B.aoM=new A.eC("1","Information We Collect","When you create an account, UniFind collects:\n\n\u2022 Your MSU email address\n\u2022 Your chosen display username\n\u2022 Listing content you post (titles, descriptions, images, prices, locations)\n\u2022 Lost & Found posts and any claim or match submissions\n\nWe do not collect payment information. All transactions are handled directly between users.",null)
B.aoS=new A.eC("2","How We Use Your Information","Your information is used to:\n\n\u2022 Create and manage your UniFind account\n\u2022 Display your listings and profile to other MSU community members\n\u2022 Facilitate lost & found claim verification\n\u2022 Improve platform functionality and user experience\n\u2022 Send account-related communications if necessary",null)
B.aoI=new A.eC("3","Information Sharing","UniFind does not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties. Your email address is used internally and is not publicly displayed \u2014 only your username is visible on listings. We may share information if required by law or MSU policy.",null)
B.ap_=new A.eC("4","Profile Pictures","Profile pictures you upload are stored locally on your device and are not uploaded to UniFind servers in the current version. Future versions may offer cloud-based profile images, covered by an updated privacy policy.",null)
B.aoL=new A.eC("5","Data Retention","Your account data and listings are retained as long as your account is active. If your account is terminated, your listings may be removed. You may request deletion of your data by contacting the UniFind team.",null)
B.aoV=new A.eC("6","Security","We take reasonable measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure. Please use a strong, unique password.",null)
B.aoQ=new A.eC("7","Cookies & Local Storage","UniFind uses local device storage (SharedPreferences) to maintain your login session across app restarts. No third-party tracking cookies or analytics tools are used.",null)
B.aoP=new A.eC("8","Your Rights","You have the right to:\n\n\u2022 Access the personal data we hold about you\n\u2022 Request correction of inaccurate data\n\u2022 Request deletion of your account and associated data\n\nTo exercise any of these rights, contact the UniFind team via your MSU email.",null)
B.aoY=new A.eC("9","Changes to This Policy","We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Continued use of UniFind after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.",null)
B.a_Q=s([B.aov,B.an,B.aoM,B.aoS,B.aoI,B.ap_,B.aoL,B.aoV,B.aoQ,B.aoP,B.aoY,B.a1,B.Kp],t.p)
B.anA=new A.oc(B.pH,"Our Mission","UniFind was created to make campus life easier at MSU. We believe everyone deserves a safe, trusted platform to buy, sell, and recover lost belongings within their own community.",!1)
B.Uc=new A.ah(63432,"MaterialIcons",!1)
B.anB=new A.oc(B.Uc,"Who We Are","We are MSU students who saw a need for a dedicated campus marketplace. UniFind is built with the MSU community in mind \u2014 every feature is designed around how students actually live on campus.",!0)
B.U9=new A.ah(63288,"MaterialIcons",!1)
B.anC=new A.oc(B.U9,"Why UniFind","Unlike other marketplaces, UniFind is exclusively for MSU community members. That means safer transactions, familiar faces, and a community you can trust. No strangers, just fellow Red Hawks.",!1)
